UPDATE companies SET agent_ids_notes = 'AI notes: ### Action Items ### Nilesh''s Background & Career Journey - **Kearney Experience (5 years):** Worked as consultant focused on consumer sector, including year-long project with Marico; gained experience across full apparel value chain from fiber to retail stores; stayed at Kearney due to strong people culture and bottom-up organization structure - **COVID Inflection Point:** Consulting remotely felt isolating compared to collaborative hotel work; prompted career transition after being last from batch to leave Kearney - **Meesho Journey (Growth Lead):** Joined initially for supply chain role but pivoted to user acquisition and growth; led team of performance marketers and influencer managers; helped Meesho become world''s most downloaded shopping app - **Three Phases at Meesho:** Started with install acquisition, expanded to new user activation (including on-app product work in pod structure), eventually led branding and creative as well as all user growth reporting to Vidit - **Key Meesho Learnings:** User-first approach with significant user research before any initiative approval; importance of strong rationale for low prices; building distribution over brand; focusing on large basket categories ### Idea Exploration & Validation Process - **Three Ideas Evaluated:** - **Co-founder Background:** Anu (life partner) brings 10 years of product experience from Gulf Talent, Insider (built live events pre-COVID), and NinjaCart (built Mandi News pricing tool for traders) ###...' WHERE id = 425 AND (agent_ids_notes IS NULL OR agent_ids_notes = '');
