UPDATE companies SET agent_ids_notes = '**Meeting Notes**: **Founder Background- **[**Karan Goyal**](https://www.linkedin.com/in/karan-goyal-6b1099188/) - Origin & early exposure: Grew up in Samana (near Patiala cantonment), surrounded by tanks and artillery; developed early fascination with defense. - Family context: Comes from a business family (yarn mill background), saw entrepreneurship at home. - Education: IIT Delhi graduate, Class of 2022. - Member of the Formula Student race car team for 4 years — hands-on hardware building, teamwork, and exposure to startup culture. - Inspired by seniors who started Baaz Bikes and Vecmocon, both now beyond Series B. - Influences: - Studied US defense-tech ecosystem — particularly Anduril (Palmer Luckey, ex-Oculus, and Palantir alumni). - Read *Kill Chain* by Anduril’s co-founder; internalized concept that modern warfare revolves around building and disrupting the “kill chain.” - Concluded that robotics will disrupt defense the most, creating room for a new “Lockheed Martin.” **Company Formation & Team** - Founded: 2022–23 after noticing drone-based drug smuggling on the India–Pakistan border. - Initial setup: Funded by founder’s father; started in a 2BHK apartment in Gurgaon converted into a workshop. - Co-founders: 5 IIT Delhi graduates. - Initially balanced jobs with building; all now full-time. - Team split: - 2 on business, investment, manufacturing, finance. - 3 on technical verticals: AI on edge (computer vision), radar development, and interceptor engineering. **Tec...' WHERE id = 433 AND (agent_ids_notes IS NULL OR agent_ids_notes = '');
